{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "下墜", "storyInfo": "嘉維爾從地下瀑布跳下，來到了際崖城，誤會解開；作為維修穹頂的替代，斯第奇希望嘉維爾等人幫忙修復鐵路橋以解決源石探測問題。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g2_fountainlake", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 謝謝你，特米米，這份恩情回到羅德島上我一定會還。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不太擅長把風，但我會努力的！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "好，我先喝一口嘗嘗！"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "end": "true", "content": "嗯，醋栗酒的口感果然夠奇怪，但是......", "joined": "好，我先喝一口嘗嘗！嗯，醋栗酒的口感果然夠奇怪，但是......"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境先生，極境！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 怎、怎麼了？我那些朋友們找過來了？你和他們說我可沒喝他們對家的酒——", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是斯第奇先生來了！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呼，找了你們好久了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 說起來，這傢伙怎麼會在這裡？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨，斯第奇。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有多少年沒見了？真不夠意思，你是不是都沒來看過我的“大水坑”？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 既然你都過來了，要一起玩嗎？衝浪區棒極了！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以幫你們偷偷把水上滑梯的限流閥打開，讓你體驗一把真正的......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不了，我趕時間。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 各位，跟我來吧，既然玩得還算開心，那接下來也該談正事了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，你總是匆匆忙忙，時間還有的是！我們完全可以......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不，我的“時間”很有限。設計代表卡奇大師身體健康，精力充沛，而我是個礦石病患，可活不了幾年。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉，我不是那個意思！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是覺得，我們可以好好聊一次，把當年的誤會......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聽好了，卡奇。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果你想找認同，際崖城的市民已經夠熱愛你了，不缺我一個。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果你想找存在感，不如再建點超級大水炮之類的玩意，漆成紅色也好，粉色也罷，我不攔著你。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 只是別在我這浪費時間了，我永遠不可能昧著良心去恭維你那些，哈，“建築作品”。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 該走了，地上人們，我會和你們講講我的規劃......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，斯第奇，聽我說——", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 卡奇，我對你的唯一建議就是，躲開我。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們各走各的路。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，找機會我們一定要聊聊你剛剛提到的超級大水炮，我很感興趣。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在此之前......你有沒有聽見什麼聲音？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 肯定是那幫醉鬼又在犯蠢吧。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#2$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道是穹頂......？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能，請相信我在工程結構上的水準。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那、那是！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下墜的感覺。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風從耳邊吹過，很吵。"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說羅德島有些奇怪的傢伙迷戀這種感覺，搞不懂他們。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於我？我會從高處往下跳只有一個理由，那就是跳下去才能解決問題。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用拳頭也好、用法杖也好、用斧頭也好。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面對問題，找到壞蛋，然後解決他。沒什麼難的，不是嗎？"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管即將看見的是什麼——"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算斧頭崩了，法杖裂了，拳頭再也握不緊。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 200.0, "g": 200.0, "b": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之去做就是了。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是陰謀也好野獸也好蘑菇也好火雨也好，還是其他什麼噁心的東西也好！", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會全都揍趴下！", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，嘉維爾，好像不太對，前面的是！", "name": "森蚺"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g2_fountainlake", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_shuihua", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "ypos": 1000.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "ypos": 1150.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_shuihua", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，我說，差不多該把我放下來了吧！", "name": "魯珀"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉。", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是個啥？瀑布？滑梯？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ape", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "xpos": 1300.0, "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 0.0, "randomness": 0.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "ypos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呦吼！", "name": "杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ape", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 1300.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 0.0, "randomness": 0.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呀，嘉維爾，你怎麼才到？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 歡迎來到杜林人的“大水坑”！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈？？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚，嘉維爾，我錯了！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呀！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以說，超級怪獸不存在，也沒有天上掉下的火雨和遮天蔽日的蘑菇？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境先生說，這是一種修辭......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一會就去揍他。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米說的也不算錯吧，杜林人的確遇到了某種麻煩。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然實在是看不出來，但起碼這位斯第奇先生是這麼聲稱的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我當然有我的理由。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以說，你們這幫自以為是的地上人又在發什麼瘋！！", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二話不說扛著斧頭闖進際崖城，聲稱什麼來幫杜林人的忙？", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開什麼玩笑，杜林人能自己解決問題，可不需要各位偉大的地上人施以援手。", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，你們身上屬於地面的骯髒和醜惡，足以玷污這座平靜的小城！", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，你是魯珀吧？你不是從地上來的？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經拋棄了地上的一切。現在的我，只是際崖城的市民罷了。", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#2$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我現在以際崖城市民的立場要求你們，離開這座城市！", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若你們依然冥頑不靈，我不介意用其他的手段驅逐你們。", "name": "魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，阿芙朵嘉，他們是我喊來的。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇......原來你回來了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你打算幹什麼，我以曾是他們一員的立場勸告你，放棄吧。借助地面上的力量只會害了際崖城。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "際崖城的市民們從未明白什麼是真正的“貪婪與陰謀”。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉，他們已經通過了一場市民表決......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我不介意再以一場市民表決否決它。這取決於杜林人的看法。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在不行的話，要是各位打算用你們地上人最擅長的流血來解決問題，我也奉陪到底。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，搞不懂你，在我看來只是一點誤會。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說阿卡胡拉地下的鄰居遇上了點麻煩，我們就來幫一把，就這麼簡單。為了他們，也為了我們自己。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，挎著把鏈鋸來鄰居家幫忙，一定只是來好心地幫我裝上桌子腿吧。說不定再用斧頭為我削個水果？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別來這一套，我親眼見過和善的使者轉瞬間就換上一副殘忍的面貌，對利益的追求和對掠奪的渴望是地上人的本性。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們或許能騙得了我善良的杜林同胞們，但你們騙不了我。我太熟悉你們的說辭了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，不管你信不信，這斧頭只是，呃，用來防身的。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果你覺得只有打架才能解決問題，那我會陪你解決。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "杜林人"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，那個拿斧頭的。", "name": "杜林人"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也太酷了吧！", "name": "興奮的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？啊......謝謝？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉，你好棒！", "name": "激動的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平常總看你拿著個本子寫寫畫畫，原來你也有這一面啊！", "name": "激動的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這得有多高？跳下來感覺如何？", "name": "興奮的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼從來沒有人想過這個主意？從瀑布的頂上跳下來！", "name": "激動的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩人是你的朋友？你這傢伙，怎麼從沒和我們說過你還有這樣的朋友！", "name": "興奮的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們可能很危險，我們不能......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能不能拜託她帶我也玩一次？", "name": "激動的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉，你這次郊遊有沒有帶來些什麼新鮮玩意？比如上次的野果！", "name": "興奮的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經好幾個小時沒見了，為了我們的再會，總得喝一杯吧！", "name": "激動的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.51, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 800.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 1000.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，等等！", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "enter": "left"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 60.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "times": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "enter": "left"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 60.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "times": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "enter": "left", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "enter2": "right", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你叫嘉維爾是嗎？我能摸摸你的斧頭嗎？很重嗎？", "name": "好奇的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，還好吧？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在有空嗎嘉維爾大姐？“大水坑”有個超好玩的秘密項目！你一定能玩出一個超酷炫的效果！", "name": "熱情的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我在際崖城的地址，如果有空的話，明天來參加我們的超級麥酒暢飲派對吧！", "name": "好奇的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還等什麼明天，不如現在我們就開始！", "name": "熱情的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好主意！", "name": "好奇的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好主意！卡奇老弟，再拿點酒來！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......杜林人怎麼回事？被極境傳染了？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米，你那是什麼表情？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾就是嘉維爾，走到哪裡都會是人群的中心呢。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，只是一群傻乎乎的人會跟在一個最傻的傢伙身後而已。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人就是擁有這樣的吸引力。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 原來她就是阿卡胡拉人經常念叨的那個“無敵的嘉維爾”。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 她為什麼會從瀑布上跳下來？你們約好的？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，大概只是物以類聚罷了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米，我被圍住了，來幫我一把！", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來了——", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這裡太亂了，我們還是換個地方吧。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g8_malistroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你就是那個杜林人。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我在阿卡胡拉的時候可是沒少聽到他們說起你的名字，嘉維爾。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說說吧，際崖城的危機到底是什麼，它會怎麼影響阿卡胡拉地區？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這個......說實話，這個話題非常複雜，涉及很多的層面，包括地理學、地質學、社會形態等等領域。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以展開講講。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 其中最麻煩的是，其實這個問題還涉及了一點點文學的領域......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......和特米米一樣，我也稍微借用了少許修辭的手法。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來你對我們說的那一套也是誇張過的？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這怎麼能算是誇張呢！我只是，呃，看法稍微歷史性地宏觀了一點點。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在千百萬年之後，隨著地殼的變化，確實有很大機率，整片雨林會沉入地下......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以揍這小鬼嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請便。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等等，等等呀！但我的確需要你們的幫忙，這件事也的確和際崖城有關！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們可以從做生意的角度來思考這個問題嘛！你們也看到了，杜林人的技術一定能給你們的雨林派上大用場！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你的那些阿卡胡拉老鄉們以後也不用再抱著幾台廢棄車床當寶貝了！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，如果真的能派上用場的話。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我可以保證，以後你們阿卡胡拉人但凡有什麼技術問題，我有問必答！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （小聲）哈，只要你們聽得懂。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我，我說，就算聽不懂我也一定儘量解釋。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就直入正題，你到底想要做什麼？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 很簡單，和我一起說服別人，把之前地震震壞的，連接城外的鐵路橋重新打通修好。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這樣，際崖城能在不去折騰那座該死穹頂的前提下，重新佈置源石勘測裝置，我也能從某個嘮叨的老頭那裡解脫出來。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 還能順便把某個擋在鐵路橋行進路線上的大滑梯炸了，簡直是一舉兩得，不，一舉三得！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇先生，為什麼不能直接修穹頂而要修鐵路呢？把那個滑梯炸了多可惜啊！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 保留那個洞並且造那個“大水坑”可是當時所有人表決通過的事情。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且修穹頂牽涉到一系列非常深奧的技術問題，和你們解釋也解釋不明白的！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 為此，我們要重新發動一場投票，來推行我們的計畫！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真不想幹啊，我挺喜歡那個滑梯，居然要炸了它......", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們杜林人的技術那麼厲害，為什麼還要阿卡胡拉人幫忙修那座橋？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......算了，告訴你們也無妨。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我作為提出重修鐵路橋這個方案的設計師，如果提案真通過了，負責人肯定也會是我。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但是！你們見過鐵路橋的圖紙嗎？那東西我以前上學的時候看到過，完全背離我極致簡約的設計理念！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那些密密麻麻的走線，那些醜陋的骨架結構！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以，所有有關橋樑鐵道設計的課，我都是睡過去的。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，你根本不會建鐵路橋？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 雖然很不想承認，但這算是我唯一的短板吧。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 於是我才請了各位對此頗有造詣的阿卡胡拉人幫忙，把這項重要的工程轉包給你們！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 怎麼樣，完美的方案。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林人的世界還真是寬容啊，這小鬼居然能順利長到這麼大......", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，你什麼意思！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，祖瑪瑪也來了，修鐵路橋的事情她大概能輕鬆解決......", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？祖瑪瑪人呢？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g1_durinstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$marketplace_intro", "key": "$marketplace_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_robotwalk", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然，我沒看錯。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......警戒。", "name": "奇怪的機械"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......小傢伙，過來！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可疑，危險！準備躲避！", "name": "奇怪的機械"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 1000.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，別跑！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 1000.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}